description:
A collection of art pieces from [[Pixiv]] artists that have received one of the highest evaluations from that community, that is, being bookmarked by over 1000 members. These pictures are usually denoted with "1000users入り" tags. For example "東方Project1000users入り":http://www.pixiv.net/tags.php?tag=%E6%9D%B1%E6%96%B9Project1000users%E5%85%A5%E3%82%8A are posts belong to the [[Touhou]] series, "オリジナル1000users入り":http://www.pixiv.net/tags.php?tag=%E3%82%AA%E3%83%AA%E3%82%B8%E3%83%8A%E3%83%AB1000users%E5%85%A5%E3%82%8A for [[original]], "VOCALOID1000users入り":http://www.pixiv.net/tags.php?tag=VOCALOID1000users%E5%85%A5%E3%82%8A for [[Vocaloid]], et cetera. Occasionally, there will be images that have achieved "5000users入り" and "10000users入り" too.

You can look for series or characters you like that belong to this pool by performing {{pool:2778 abc_xyz}} search (replace abc_xyz with what you want).

For any group of images that qualify, only the first page in its respective pool is included, and the pool name will be mentioned in this description:
